    PIRACY

    copying  or  using  an  illegal  copy  of  this  game is a crime. More
    importantly, copying games means that software houses are  finding  it
    increasingly  difficult  to support the Amiga. If you want to continue
    playing games of the same quality then buy them, don`t rip them off.

    A copy protection has been added to  this  game  so  that  it  is  not
    possible  to copy this game using the normal Working methods or any of
    the various backup devices available.

